  origins and background originally formed in 1994 as an octet ( under the name galactic prophylactic ) and including singer chris lane and guitarist rob gowen , the group was soon pared down to a sextet of : guitarist jeff raines , bassist robert mercurio , drummer stanton moore , hammond organist rich vogel , theryl declouet on vocals , and later adding saxophonist ben ellman .

outer space : galactic light 's " shift " toward this color of the visible spectrum shows that the universe is expanding

